<refsect2 id="fp-err" role="macro">
<title>fp_err</title>
<indexterm zone="fp-err"><primary>fp_err</primary></indexterm>
<programlisting language="C">#define fp_err g_critical
</programlisting>
<para>Same as <link linkend="g-critical"><function>g_critical()</function></link>. In the future, this might be changed to a
<link linkend="g-assert"><function>g_assert()</function></link> instead, so bear this in mind when adding those calls
to your driver.</para>
</refsect2>

